ence to the lives of people affected by armed conflict.">Planned giving</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container pull-right hidden-xs hidden-sm"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/donate" class="bg-red nav-link-main">Donate</a></div></div></div></div> </nav></div><div class="region region-content"><div id="fullpage"> <section class="clearfix section first-section " id="what-we-do"><div class="wwd-inner"><div class="header-wrapper visible-sm visible-xs"><header class="site-header"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-4 slogan-logo"><div class="logo-wrapper"><div id="logo"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en" class="logo"><img src="/sites/default/themes/icrc_theme/images/en/logo-small.png" alt="International Committee of the Red Cross"/></a></div><div class="slogan font-sm-18"><h1 class="font-sm-18"> International Committee of the Red Cross</h1></div></div></div><div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-8 right-content"><div class="visible-sm visible-xs list-languages"> <select class="styled-language-select i-arrow-down-after redirection-select"><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en" selected="selected">EN</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/fr">FR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/es">ES</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/pt">PT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/zh">ZH</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ar">AR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ru">RU</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/de">DE</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/it">IT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/languages">Other</option> </select></div></div></div></div></header></div><div class="fill section-first-main"><div class="video-section"><div class="video-wrapper responsive-video-container video-available"> <video data-keepplaying data-autoplay loop muted poster="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT"> <source data-src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/homepage_files/what-we-do-video_0.mp4" type="video/mp4" /> </video><div class="image"> <img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/homepage_files/icrc-car-syria_1.jpg?itok=sydI4NeT" alt="icrc-car-syria"/></div><div class="video-text-wrapper"><div class="video-text"> <a href="/en/what-we-do/video" class="lightbox-embed-video youtube"><span class="thumbnail-video-button"></span></a><div class="main-text">On the ground in over 90 countries - neutral, impartial, and independent - we are the International Committee of the Red Cross</div></div></div></div></div><div class="text-section"><div class="container fill"><div class="row fill"><div class="text-wrapper-outer fill"><div class="text-wrapper"><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/en/who-we-are" class="">Learn about us </a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>We work around the world helping people affected by conflict and armed violence, and promoting the <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/rules-of-war" target="_self">rules of war</a>.</p></div></div><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/en/who-we-are/jobs" class="">Work with us </a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>Do you have a strong humanitarian motivation? Learn more about how to join the ICRC.</p></div></div><div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 text-block"> <a class="title-text" href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/" class="">Support us </a><div class="red-divider"></div><div class="sub-text"><p>Help families and communities affected by armed conflict in conflict regions all over the world.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section> <section class="clearfix section ss " id="highlight"><div class="fill "><div class="video-section no-video-available"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day" target="_self" ><div class="highlight-image-wrapper"><div class="image " style="background-image: url('https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/special_page_image/public/home_carousel_slide/image/20200202_ammar_saboh_-_harasta-7_0.jpg?itok=qLpseX8O');"></div></div> </a><div class="highlight-text-wrapper"><div class="highlight-text-inner JsClickParent" data-ClickLink="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day" target="_self" class="highlight-title" ><span class="crnr-brdr crnr-brdr-tl"></span>Syria: As economic crisis bites, lack of humanitarian access costs lives every day<span class="crnr-brdr crnr-brdr-br"></span></a><div class="highlight-fields JsClickParent" data-ClickLink="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day"><div class="highlight-share hidden-sm hidden-xs JsClickParent" data-ClickLink="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day"><div class="social-icons-theme2 clearfix font-xs-12 font-md-18 JsClickDisabled"><div class="corner-border social-icon-main"><div class="corner-border-inner"> <span class="social-icon2 social-icon-bg small-icon i-share"></span></div></div><div class="corner-border social-icons-group hidden"><div class="corner-border-inner"><div class="social-icon-bg"> <a class="social-icon2 i-twitter" href="https://twitter.com/share?url=https://www.icrc.org/en/document/syria-economic-crisis-bites-lack-humanitarian-access-costs-lives-every-day" target="_blank" title="Share on Twitter" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Social Share', 'twitter', 'https://www.icrc.org/en/document/syria-economic-crisis-bit