rc.org/ilot/" target="_blank">Israel and the occupied territories</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/new-delhi/" target="_blank">New Delhi</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/gphi2/" target="_blank">Global Partnership for Humanitarian Impact and Innovation</a></li><li> <a href="http://kr.icrc.org/" target="_blank">Republic of Korea</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/law-and-policy/" target="_blank">Humanitarian law and policy</a></li><li></li><li> <a href="http://jp.icrc.org/" target="_blank">Japan</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/th/" target="_blank">Bangkok</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/indonesia/" target="_blank">Jakarta</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/somalia/" target="_blank">Somalia</a></li><li> <a href="http://moveability.icrc.org/" target="_blank">MoveAbility</a></li><li> <a href="http://blogs.icrc.org/alinsani/" target="_blank">Alinsani</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> </nav><div class="social-icons clear"><div class="container"><div class="row"> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-twitter i-twitter-color-hover" href="https://twitter.com/icrc" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">Twitter</span></a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-facebook i-facebook-color-hover" href="https://www.facebook.com/icrc" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">Facebook</span></a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-instagram i-instagram-color-hover" href="https://www.instagram.com/ICRC/" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">Instagram</span></a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-linkedin i-linkedin-color-hover" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/icrc" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span></a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-youtube i-youtube-color-hover" href="https://www.youtube.com/icrcfilms" target="_blank"><span class="sr-only">YouTube</span></a> <a class="social-icon img-circle i-social-media-dashboard i-social-media-dashboard-color-hover" href="https://www.icrc.org/